  "detailed_description": "<strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >DobbyxEscape: Pirate Adventure</h2></strong><br>Ahoy, Me Hearties!<br><br>Tommy wants to be a pirate when he grows up!<br><br>With the help of a Blue Moon, the tap of his magic wand and his great great great grandfather's pirate hat, his dreams come true!<br><br>Follow Tommy on the adventure of a lifetime where he meets the legendary pirate Blackbeard!<br><br>All Hands Ahoy!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353650/extras/9fbe46b33174a5dfd89e5a7db26829d9.poster.avif?t=1680257718\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353650/extras/9fbe46b33174a5dfd89e5a7db26829d9.webm?t=1680257718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353650/extras/9fbe46b33174a5dfd89e5a7db26829d9.mp4?t=1680257718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features:</h2></strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Room Escape game!<br></li><li>Six locations to discover!<br></li><li>Beautiful graphics bring the game to life!<br></li><li>Many items to collect and puzzles to solve!<br></li><li>Fun soundtrack and sound effects!</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353650/extras/6798d224f742237354ba9045c0c3d6ca.poster.avif?t=1680257718\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353650/extras/6798d224f742237354ba9045c0c3d6ca.webm?t=1680257718\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2353650/extras/6798d224f742237354ba9045c0c3d6ca.mp4?t=1680257718\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
